      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine and a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example exhibits excellent throttle response thanks to its individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated double-VANOS system. The chassis integrity is verified with a reinforced rear subframe and refreshed RTABs, ensuring the Variable M Differential Lock translates power to the tarmac without deflection. Performance is anchored by a factory-spec suspension geometry and ventilated compound rotors. While showing minor patina consistent with enthusiast use, the powertrain remains robust with consistent compression across all cylinders and a strictly followed 10W-60 lubrication schedule.",
